{"tid":538374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買春當獎勵！拿第一名就有特別輔導","createTime":"2018-01-23T14:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T09:46:55.000Z","uid":94906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec66f2041a6a71a8de20585ba00bdb35961a08b","tid":538374,"uid":94906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n將孩子教成資優生，什麼手段都可以原諒嗎？南韓一名補習班名師非常有名，資質普通的學生到他手裡都可以成為資優生，然而最近卻被爆出，學生們努力上進的原因全都是因為想要名師的獎勵，而這獎勵竟是帶他們到風俗店好好享受一番。<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓MBN（Maeil Broadcasting Network）頻道報導，該名補教名師號稱可以拯救所有成績不好的學生，也的確有漂亮成效，因此許多家長爭相將孩子送給他指導，且家長們發現孩子成績的確「突飛猛進」，然而就在此刻，家長們在網路上發現一段偷拍影片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該段影片是在某風俗店內的偷拍畫面，家長們驚異發現，影片中的主角們竟然就是自己的孩子，事情曝光，原來名師以「特殊獎勵」來鼓勵學生努力讀書，只要拿到第一名或模範生資格，就會和他們約「特別輔導」，就是帶他們到風俗店好好享受，因此學生們才會用功念書。<br />\n<br />\n家長們發現老師「買春當獎勵」的事實後，氣到告上法院，而影片作證，名師也坦承不諱，如今名師已遭南韓當地法院判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd8a83d799184cd8be72c152b887751045c1900","tid":538374,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2133f7207598696ecb3c0ef54da010d7905fa634","tid":538374,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"告乜撚<br />\n成績真係有好到嚄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27484c4e0616442ea9e3b3dae0a448cecb14867d","tid":538374,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"過橋抽板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad89d0ae52d729e343b83a1df278df7fcce7fe8","tid":538374,"uid":168026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"家長發現流出片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a08c548d9cb697efc4ee9d8d525abb3c319a463","tid":538374,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"喺韓國攞唔到好成績入唔到名牌大學等食屎都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a0c358e988f77ba09c386d4b073773c98cc693","tid":538374,"uid":139815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"叫雞有咩問題"},{"pid":"7a149d86c6f3173b9b2c64ea3542e1945ed1e6ea","tid":538374,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a08c548d9cb697efc4ee9d8d525abb3c319a463","tid":538374,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"喺韓國攞唔到好成績入唔到名牌大學等食屎都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"睇過新聞話d老母會去學校門口跪地係咁拜祈求考試順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b067a0ac9461f79af53738600879f2a1168396b2","tid":538374,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"可以告啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請人叫雞罪？"}]}